<div class="refunds-services-wrapper">
  <div class="container container--takeover-custom">
    <header class="page__header">
      <h1 class="page__title heading h1">{{ page.title }}</h1>
    </header>
  </div>

  <div class="container-wide returns-grid-3">  
    <div>
      <img src="https://wellwise.s3.amazonaws.com/shipping/1.png" alt=""/>
      <h2 class="heading">
        Return by Mail
      </h2>
      <p>
        All returns of online transactions are to be returned by mail only. Customers will have 90 days after receiving a product to initiate a return online.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img src="https://wellwise.s3.amazonaws.com/shipping/2.png" alt=""/>
      <h2 class="heading">
        Cost to Return
      </h2>
      <p>
        Returns are free, however not all products are eligible. See the exclusions section for more details.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <img src="https://wellwise.s3.amazonaws.com/shipping/3.png" alt=""/>
      <h2 class="heading">
        Return Tender and Timeline
      </h2>
      <p>
        Customers will receive the refund in the same payment method used for the purchase. After the product has been delivered to our return facility, funds should be returned within approximately 10-15 business days depending on your bank.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  {%- if false -%}
  <div class="container temp-delay">
    <h3 class="heading">
    	Temporary Delay in Return Processing - Updated September 21, 2020
    </h3>
    <p>
      Due to new COVID related procedures in Return Handling we are experiencing delays in Return Processing. We expect all delayed returns to be completed as of October 2, 2020 and regular processing times to resume after that date.
    </p>
  </div>
  {%- endif -%}
  <div class="container init-returns">
    <h2 class="heading">
    	How to Initiate a Return.
    </h2>
    <p>
      An online return requires an RMA (Return Merchandise Authorization) Number.
    </p>
    
    <h3 class="heading">
    	Ways to request an RMA number:
    </h3>
    <div class="flex-ways">
      <div>
        <h4 class="heading">
          Online (Purchased with Account)
        </h4>
        
        <ul>
          <li>Visit your Account Page</li>
          <li>Click on the “Order History” section</li>
          <li>Locate your order and click return on the item(s)</li>
          <li>You will be sent an email with an RMA within 2 business days.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="heading">
          Online (Purchased As Guest)
        </h4>
        
        <ul>
          <li>Open your Order Confirmation Email</li>
          <li>Click on the Order Number Link</li>
          <li>You will be taken to wellwise.ca and shown your order</li>
          <li>Click return on the item(s)</li>
          <li>You will be sent an email with an RMA within 2 business days.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p class="heading any-issues-lbl">
      If you have issues with either method please email <a href="mailto:support@wellwise.ca">support@wellwise.ca</a>.
    </p>
    
    <a href="/pages/contact-us" class="button button--primary">
      Customer service
    </a>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container multi-box">
    <h2 class="heading">
      Multi-box products.
    </h2>
    <p>
      If the product was shipped to you in multiple boxes, please wait until you’ve received the final box before making a return. The return period will start after you get the final package
    </p>
  </div>
